接口 ClientRequest.HeadersBuilder<B extends ClientRequest.HeadersBuilder<B>>

    public static interface ClientRequest.HeadersBuilder<B extends ClientRequest.HeadersBuilder<B>>
    Defines a builder that adds headers to the request.
